{"tid":1949130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★日本年輕人：去舞廳說可以「跳走肺炎」、「年輕人不會染病無有怕」.....","createTime":"2020-03-29T12:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T12:29:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45c8994f2a1cf0fea6a731f9c1fcf25960569191","tid":1949130,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200329/320989233533816832.jpeg/C5d-tVr8-WjG7ZnfyO9KmlaGvPuAM0SsTQYKOE0GCjg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200329%2F320989233533816832.jpeg%2FC5d-tVr8-WjG7ZnfyO9KmlaGvPuAM0SsTQYKOE0GCjg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4328aa4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東京TBS新聞訪問一對正前往澀谷舞廳的年輕人，其中一人說笑般的表示「會否怕舞廳會染病？跳舞可以跳走肺炎！」<br />\n<br />\n日視新聞（日TV）亦走訪東京各地，訪問到有10多歲的年輕人稱「年輕人不會染病無有怕」、亦有因為「在家中放假太久所以想外出」。日本現正停課，年輕人本應都留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n小池百合子在3月27日應日本放送協會（NHK）訪問，說明疫情在東京的影響。小池在節目上特別點名年輕人，呼籲他們應留在家中：「現在是決定疫情會否進一步擴散的重要階段，為了保護自己，亦為了避免自己感染病毒而無自覺地散播病毒感染他人，年輕人應避免外出。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/454187/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E7%85%A7%E5%8E%BB%E8%88%9E%E5%BB%B3%E8%AA%AA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5-%E8%B7%B3%E8%B5%B0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F454187%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2587%25B6%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E7%2585%25A7%25E5%258E%25BB%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=870cc794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/454187/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E7%85%A7%E5%8E%BB%E8%88%9E%E5%BB%B3%E8%AA%AA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5-%E8%B7%B3%E8%B5%B0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E</a>"},{"pid":"ae43dea38eff585885b599c2da665a587d48be2e","tid":1949130,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ybvW7o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ybvW7o.gif&h=1c17ca89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26198b908219221c3a420af0793659231c87de9a","tid":1949130,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"595fab054555bd8878b744ae5face5d9d6cd0363","tid":1949130,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"昭和以後冇日本"}]}